du.hk/Lexis/lexi-mf/search.php?word=%E5%A5%AA</a><br />\n<br />\n奪取本身無話一定要用暴力對任何人，中文黎講，強行進入如果你無人係度阻止都可以叫奪取，仲有當時新聞直播明明就係講「我地一齊進入廣場」，根本無人要求對阻止嘅人使用暴力。"},{"pid":"d36e5248c0ca04ced6d17bb8cdd70db5704bc56e","tid":352920,"uid":52590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T07:55:47.000Z","msg":"真係好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0cad007b589e444221f95a07419fc2b1612516","tid":352920,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T07:57:30.000Z","msg":"口講「奪」已經唔係和理非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341348c786b7db04c63d87c49b1318d43803cc8e","tid":352920,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T07:59:43.000Z","msg":"奪冠你就仆街啦，告得你搶劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"997195b678d2b605989b4016d62d4f311505693d","tid":352920,"uid":28765,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T08:00:06.000Z","msg":"橫刀奪愛算唔算刑事 又奪又刀"},{"pid":"c51703807c63ed1dbe4fd4780d8d2268bace1603","tid":352920,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T08:02:24.000Z","msg":"控方想講咩都係佢自由，主要睇法官點判"},{"pid":"0067ce5728e08179e6fb3b6f8936da822aaa9654","tid":352920,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T08:02:35.000Z","msg":"阿律政屍代表係咪細個跌親個腦，咁撚戇尻都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e70ae280327c2c42d85203420726b15991cce6e","tid":352920,"uid":54344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T08:12:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>控方想講咩都係佢自由，主要睇法官點判</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>阿律政屍代表係咪細個跌親個腦，咁撚戇尻都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀咁多年書 你同我上庭9up？"},{"pid":"b37f767aa274d3658c84a92e6e215816b59db1d9","tid":352920,"uid":53577,"like":